<div class="jumbotron" style = "margin-right: 100px; margin-left: 100px">
  <h1>Welcome to Socialize.me</h1>
  <p> A modern client for your favorite social networks. All in one place.</p>
  <p> Start using it now by choosing your preferred social network.</p>
  <p> <em><strong>We're better than hootsuite</strong></em> </p>
</div>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <%= image_tag "home_timeline.png", :alt => "Home Timeline"%>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Home timeline</h3>
        <p> Check the last updates of the people you are following and keep track of everything you like </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <%= image_tag "user_timeline.jpg", :alt => "User Timeline"%>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>User timeline</h3>
        <p> You can see your last tweets </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-sm-6 col-md-4">
    <div class="thumbnail">
      <%= image_tag "custom-search.png", :alt => "User Timeline"%>
      <div class="caption">
        <h3>Custom search</h3>
        <p> Look for tweets about anything you want </p>
        <p> You can look for people, hashtags or any topic </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

